{"tid":1674694,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"歡樂天地試業中, 大家去九龍灣 EMAX 朝勝","createTime":"2019-10-25T10:59:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-26T11:04:35.000Z","uid":210037,"like":6,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"3047245223ef203fdc49ce824a11d3a71f2b5f0c","tid":1674694,"uid":210037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T10:59:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6nF0o3e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6nF0o3e.jpg&h=aad0390d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n是咁的, 今日得閒就去會一會 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ShUgGQU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FShUgGQU.jpg&h=839a4944&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n20 年前 2 蚊一個幣, 20 年後都係 2 蚊一個幣, 不過啲幣大幅貶值 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PuW635d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPuW635d.jpg&h=ee9190e9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n經典賽馬機, 仍然係 8 個幣一區, 贏咗有公仔 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yWiAXqY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyWiAXqY.jpg&h=c031a085&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/c5xiaMe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fc5xiaMe.jpg&h=3f783a60&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n經典大阪牙, 6 個幣一局, 6 球射穿牙 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bgmnCrQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbgmnCrQ.jpg&h=cd86572a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n經典碌波, 6 個幣一局, 個波好膠 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0Yk7Oy7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0Yk7Oy7.jpg&h=945f28ab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n經典保齡球, 不過我無技術, 無玩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GMJUtzy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGMJUtzy.jpg&h=71e6d0d9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n大量伏機, 幫大家啲幣對沖 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cTHqAe1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcTHqAe1.jpg&h=4b19f466&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n官方 FB 小編推介, 每局 1 幣, 比較容易取票 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e4cef57206b27ac1e4900743193fcd9076a865f","tid":1674694,"uid":181092,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T11:04:26.000Z","msg":"垃圾到爆炸，d機又係殘體字，見到唔開胃<br />\n同以前無得比"},{"pid":"793c442a0aa38475f0b29e488016f4d0f9f353cd","tid":1674694,"uid":210037,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"1e4cef57206b27ac1e4900743193fcd9076a865f","tid":1674694,"uid":181092,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T11:04:26.000Z","msg":"垃圾到爆炸，d機又係殘體字，見到唔開胃<br />\n同以前無得比"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T11:07:27.000Z","msg":"唔計殘體字, 淨係伏機都一大批, 夾公仔要 10 個幣 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9cff24d8c94a1d92b72d94f8c6f7ad7fa257ac0","tid":1674694,"uid":44622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T12:02:57.000Z","msg":"靜過鬼"},{"pid":"2d4519769c689938fe5e1fbdc4060f68cafe1b39","tid":1674694,"uid":44747,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T12:04:22.000Z","msg":"都搵唔返以前果種快樂"},{"pid":"e2b5732c4b1488465075489870548c852fc46fcc","tid":1674694,"uid":36435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T12:04:34.000Z","msg":"D票有咩換"},{"pid":"2578d5cb7d123a9220df9b128d3fd7ed25afcf58","tid":1674694,"uid":279356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTim